-- Gupta Says He Shouldn’t Have to Pay Goldman Sachs for Legal Fees
-- B y   B o b   V a n   V o r i s
-- 2012-12-14T22:24:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-14/gupta-says-he-shouldn-t-have-to-pay-goldman-sachs-for-legal-fees.html
Rajat Gupta, convicted of insider
trading crimes, said he shouldn’t have to pay $7 million
restitution for legal fees to Goldman Sachs Group Inc., where he
was a former director.  To contact the reporter on this story:
